### Dexie Export/Import TypeScript Interface Definition

Source: https://github.com/dexie/dexie.js/blob/master/addons/dexie-export-import/README.md

Defines the TypeScript interfaces that are extended on the Dexie and DexieConstructor objects when the dexie-export-import module is imported. This specifies the `export` and `import` methods available on Dexie instances and the static `import` method on the DexieConstructor, including their parameters and return types.

```APIDOC
declare module 'dexie' {
  // Extend methods on db
  interface Dexie {
    export(options?: ExportOptions): Promise<Blob>;
    import(blob: Blob, options?: ImportOptions): Promise<void>;
  }
  interface DexieConstructor {
    import(blob: Blob, options?: StaticImportOptions): Promise<Dexie>;
  }
}
```

