### Define Dexie.js Export Options Interface

Source: https://github.com/dexie/dexie.js/blob/master/addons/dexie-export-import/README.md

Defines the TypeScript interface for `ExportOptions` used with `Dexie.prototype.export()`. These options control transaction behavior, chunking of rows, pretty JSON formatting, filtering, and progress callbacks during export.

```ts
export interface ExportOptions {
  noTransaction?: boolean;
  numRowsPerChunk?: number;
  prettyJson?: boolean;
  filter?: (table: string, value: any, key?: any) => boolean;
  progressCallback?: (progress: ExportProgress) => boolean;
}
```

